<div id="review_1017904232" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1017904232" />
    <a title="BookOfCinz" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/9750143-bookofcinz"><img alt="BookOfCinz" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1633189811p2/9750143.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1017904232?book_show_action=true">Aug 05, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="BookOfCinz" class="user" itemprop="url" name="BookOfCinz" href="/user/show/9750143-bookofcinz">BookOfCinz</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9750143-bookofcinz?shelf=inspiring-and-motivating">inspiring-and-motivating</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9750143-bookofcinz?shelf=life-changing">life-changing</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9750143-bookofcinz?shelf=cant-shut-up-about-this">cant-shut-up-about-this</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9750143-bookofcinz?shelf=absolute-favorite">absolute-favorite</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9750143-bookofcinz?shelf=2019-reads">2019-reads</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9750143-bookofcinz?shelf=self-improvement">self-improvement</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9750143-bookofcinz?shelf=re-reads">re-reads</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1017904232" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10388654492393788425">2019<br/>A timely reminder that you can change your life at anytime. <br/><br/>January 14, 2018<br/>&quot;The Monk Who Sold My Ferrari&quot; is one of my favorite books to (re)read at the start of the year. This book never disappoints and it was great getting a reminder of all the things I need to focus on to make this a great year. Too often we get all caught up in the rat race and as this book succinctly puts it, &quot;even if you win the rat race you are still a rat&quot;.<br/>I do try daily to incorporate the 10 Rituals of Radiant Livi</span>
  <span id="freeText10388654492393788425" style="display:none">2019<br />A timely reminder that you can change your life at anytime. <br /><br />January 14, 2018<br />"The Monk Who Sold My Ferrari" is one of my favorite books to (re)read at the start of the year. This book never disappoints and it was great getting a reminder of all the things I need to focus on to make this a great year. Too often we get all caught up in the rat race and as this book succinctly puts it, "even if you win the rat race you are still a rat".<br />I do try daily to incorporate the 10 Rituals of Radiant Living, it really helps putting these daily rituals at the focal point of your life, it will really improve your year. <br />Must. Read.<br /><br /><br />This book is life changing. It changed my life. CHANGED. <br />Everyone should read it and keep re-reading it. <br /><br />Read this book for the first time in August 2014. I decided to re-read it for the start of the new year and I was not disappointed. This is a life changing book, providing you follow the instructions given by the Monk. The book outlines simple practical steps on how to change your life and keep it changed. <br />Go read it!</span>
  <a data-text-id="10388654492393788425" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
